experiences.jobDescription:
As a senior software development engineer, I’m responsible for designing, developing, building, maintaining and troubleshooting a variety of Globys B2B services and ERP products. The primary tasks involve designing, developing, building and deploying
  (1) stateless, data-driven, modular and robust ETL processing software;
  (2) distributed, robust and extensible Account Receivable payment solution;
  (3) continuous delivery solution for cloud services;
  (4) ERP cloud service integration with Globys data source, Quickbooks Online and Oracle NetSuite.
 The primary skill stack covers AWS, Azure, NodeJS/JavaScript, ERP application development  (QuickBooks Online, Xero, MYOB, etc), SQL Server, MongoDB, HTTPS/SSL, JSON/XML.

As a senior software development engineer, I’m responsible for designing, developing, building, maintaining and troubleshooting UIE Cloud Connect web services. The primary tasks involve
    design, develop, build and deploy new service features such as big data processing, user management, application catalog, logging, cron tasks, etc;
    troubleshoot problems, resolve and fix bugs;
    document requirements, specifications and design blueprints.
 The primary skill stack covers Java, NodeJS, JavaScript/TypeScript, MySQL, MongoDB, Message Queue, HTTPS/SSL, JSON/XML, Maven, data modeling, Git.
